parameters: \fs[18]Alright! I want to play all the events this year without missing a single one!
\fs[28]好！今年也要一个都不错过地把项目都玩一遍！
\fs[18](Why don't I have any impressions of this?)
\fs[18](I don't remember the registration for the school festival at all...)
\fs[28]（我完全不记得有学园祭报名这件事啊？）
\fs[18](The past few days feel so muddled.)
\fs[18](I feel like I can't even remember what happened yesterday.....)
\fs[28]（感觉就连昨天的事情都有点记不清了……）
\fs[18](Hope I can help out next year, else I'll really feel embarrassed...)
\fs[28]（希望下年能帮上忙吧，不然真的连自己都不好意思了……）

\fs[28]（好像今晚有烟火大会，应该是在操场那边举行？）
\fs[18](I'll head there after going through most of the booths. )
\fs[28]（等摊位这边玩得差不多就过去吧）
\}Welcome to the Literature Club's game booth!
\}\#Ah~ Since you're here at our booth...

\{
\#啊~既然你来到了我们的摊位……
\}\#You're most likely someone that likes reading books!

\{
\#想必你也是喜欢看书的人吧！
\}\#So, with the theme of books in mind
\}\#Sci-fi masterpieces that open up your mind?

\{
\#是让你脑洞大开的科幻巨作？

\{
\#抑或是fa(发?)人深省的哲学沉思录？
\}\#Whatever topic you like, you can come to the Literature Club to talk about it!

\{
\#不管是喜欢什么题材，都可以来文学部交流一下哦！
\}\#Talking endlessly when I mention these things

\{
\#一提到这些就滔滔不绝了起来
\}\#Our Literature Club has encountered a huge crisis recently

\{
\#最近我们文学部遇到了一个大大大危机
\}\#We are attempting to write a medieval fantasy adventure novel

\{
\#我们在尝试写一本中古魔幻冒险题材小说
\}\#But we're not sure where to start...
\}\#So the theme of our game for the school festival is...

\{
\#所以我们这次学园祭游戏的主题就是……
\}\#Writing the setting for the script together! ! !
\}\#(Isn't this perfectly justifiable as 摸鱼?)

\{
\#(这不就是名正言顺的摸鱼吗？)
\}\#You were born on the ancient continent, Cabres.
\{\#你出生在一片名叫卡布雷斯的远古大陆
\}\#This continent was split into 4 great empires. You were born in...
\{\#这片大陆被分成了4大帝国。你出生在……

"You were born in Fordrain Village. Like everyone else here, you were born with the head of a fish and a human body. You are a born natural when it comes to swimming, but you were caught by people on the shore.|你出生在了福德雷恩村。你和这个地方的其他人一样，长着鱼头和人身，而且你从小就特别会游泳，但是你老是被岸上的人钓上来。"

"You were born in Lavanian Fort. Like everyone else here, you were born with a butt for your face, and a face on your butt. You are exceptionally resistant to heat.|你出生在了拉瓦尼亚堡。你和这个地方的其他人一样，屁股长在了你的脸上，脸长在了屁股上，而且你非常耐热。"

"You were born in Iccypunk. Like everyone else here, you look like an ice cream cone, and are good at generating ice cream cones from your nose and stabbing enemies to death with them.|你出生在了埃斯朋克镇。你和这个地方的其他人一样，长得跟甜筒雪糕一样，而且你擅长用鼻涕做成冰锥捅死敌人。"
"You were born in Woodin Castle. Like everyone else here, you look like a tree stump, and passing travelers love to peepee on you.|你出生在了梧丁城。你和这个地方的其他人一样，长得像个树桩，而且过路的旅行者都喜欢在你这里尿尿。"
\}\#The environment you were born in was...
